text: Luna I qui inciderit, difficile euadetSe þe afealð, earfoðlice he ætwint.
Luna II, cito consurgetraðe he arisþ.
Luna III, non eundethe ne ætwint.
Luna IIII, laboret et surgethe swincð and arisð.
Luna V, tricabit et surgethe sipað and arisð.
Luna VI, non euadethe ne ætwint.
Luna VII, medicina sanabiturmid læcedome he bið gehæled.
Luna VIII, diu languet et surgetlange he adlað and arisð.
Luna IX, languethe adlað.
Luna X diu egrotatlange he siclað.
Luna XI, periculo periclitaton frecednesse he dyrfð.
Luna XII, surgethe arisþ.
Luna XIII, alignot tempus egrotatsumne timan he sicclað.
Luna XIIII, laborat et surgethe swincð and arisþ.
Luna XV periclitathe dyrfð.
Luna XVI, locum mitabit et surgetstowe he awent and arisð.
Luna XVII, tricabit et surgethe sipað and arisþ.
Luna XVIII, laborabit et surgethe swincð and arisð.
Luna XIX, similitereallswa.
Luna XX, similitereallswa.
Luna XXI, rem adiuuabitðingc he fultumað.
Luna XXII, languet et surgethe adlað and arisþ.
Luna XXIII, similitereallswa.
Luna XXIIII, diu languetlange he adlað.
Luna XXV, languet et morieturadlað and he swelt.
Luna XXVI, languethe adlað.
Luna XXVII, tricabit et surgethe sipað and arisþ.
Luna XXVIII, eger multum iacebit et morieturseoc swiðe he lið and swylt.
Luna XXIX, eger euadetseoc ætwint.
Luna XXX, eger laborabit et surgetseoc he swincð and arisð.
